                    "text_description" : "어떤 식을 $A$라고 하면 \\[ \\begin{array}{l} A-\\left(-x^{2}+2 x-4\\right)=6 x^{2}+3 x-1 \\text { 에서 } \\\\ \\begin{aligned} A & =6 x^{2}+3 x-1+\\left(-x^{2}+2 x-4\\right) \\\\ & =6 x^{2}+3 x-1-x^{2}+2 x-4 \\\\ & =5 x^{2}+5 x-5 \\end{aligned} \\end{array} \\] 따라서 바르게 계산한 식은 \\[ \\begin{array}{l} 5 x^{2}+5 x-5+\\left(-x^{2}+2 x-4\\right) \\\\ =5 x^{2}+5 x-5-x^{2}+2 x-4 \\\\ =4 x^{2}+7 x-9 \\end{array} \\]"
